---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Privacy Policy';
const pageDescription = 'How Listwin Ventures collects, uses, shares, and safeguards personal information.';
---

<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <article class="space-y-6 text-base leading-7 text-ink/80">
    <header class="space-y-2">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>
        We value your privacy very highly. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully before using the listwinventures.com
        website (the “Website”) operated by Listwin Ventures, a Limited Liability Company formed in California, United States
        (“us, we, our”), as this Privacy Policy contains important information regarding your privacy and how we may use the
        information we collect about you.
      </p>
      <p>
        Your access to or use of the Website is conditional upon your acceptance of and compliance with this Privacy Policy. This
        Privacy Policy applies to everyone, including but not limited to visitors, users, and others, who wish to access or use the
        Website. By accessing or using the Website, you agree to be bound by this Privacy Policy. If you disagree with any part of
        this Privacy Policy, you do not have our permission to access or use the Website.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">What information we collect and store</h2>
      <p>We collect and store any and all information that you enter on this Website, including:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
        <li>Identifying information – Name</li>
        <li>Identifying information – IP address</li>
        <li>Identifying information – Email address</li>
        <li>Identifying information – Device identifier</li>
        <li>Internet or other electronic activity – Information regarding your interaction with our website or application</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">With whom we share your personal information</h2>
      <p>
        We share the personal information listed above with third parties for purposes of operating, improving, and protecting the
        Website, as well as complying with legal obligations.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">How we protect your personal information</h2>
      <p>
        We protect and safeguard your personal information by using SSL encryption or other secure technologies when receiving or
        sending personal information beyond internal networks.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This Website collects cookies. A cookie is a small piece of data sent from a website and stored on your device by your
        browser. Please visit our Cookie Policy to learn more about what cookies we collect, why we collect them, and how to change
        your cookie settings.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Children’s privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This Website is intended for use by a general audience and does not offer services to children. Should a child whom we know
        to be under 18 send personal information to us, we will use that information only to respond to that child to inform them
        that they cannot use this Website.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Analytics programs</h2>
      <p>
        This Website uses Google Analytics to collect information about you and your behaviors. If you would like to opt-out of
        Google Analytics, please visit <a class="text-brand underline" href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout/">https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout/</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Information retention</h2>
      <p>We retain all of the information that we collect until we no longer need the information to contact you.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Your rights</h2>
      <p>All visitors or users of this Website have the following rights with regard to their personal information:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
        <li>The right to access the personal information that we hold about you.</li>
        <li>The right to receive the personal information that we hold about you in a portable format.</li>
        <li>The right to ask us to transmit your personal information to another provider, where technically feasible.</li>
        <li>The right to request that we amend any of the information that we have collected about you.</li>
        <li>The right to withdraw your consent to the processing of your personal information.</li>
        <li>The right to request that we restrict the processing of your personal information.</li>
        <li>The right to request that we delete some or all of the personal information that we have collected about you.</li>
        <li>The right to lodge a complaint regarding our data practices with competent authorities.</li>
        <li>The right to opt out of direct marketing, data sales, location tracking, profiling, and automated decision making.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Exercising your rights</h2>
      <p>You may exercise the rights specified above by submitting a consumer request to:</p>
      <address class="space-y-1 not-italic">
        <div>Listwin Ventures</div>
        <div><a class="text-brand underline" href="mailto:privacy@listwinventures.com">privacy@listwinventures.com</a></div>
        <div>United States</div>
        <div><a class="text-brand underline" href="https://listwinventures.com">listwinventures.com</a></div>
      </address>
      <p>
        We will need to verify your identity prior to processing your request. Please include your name, IP address, and email
        address in the request. We generally respond within 30 days and will notify you if more time is required. Certain legal
        exceptions may allow us to deny a request; if that occurs, we will explain the basis for the denial.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Accountability</h2>
      <p>
        The following person is accountable and responsible for our privacy practices and procedures:
        <br />
        Listwin Ventures – <a class="text-brand underline" href="mailto:privacy@listwinventures.com">privacy@listwinventures.com</a>
      </p>
      <p>
        You may lodge a complaint with us using the contact above. Residents of Canada may also lodge a complaint with the Office
        of the Privacy Commissioner of Canada by calling 1-800-282-1376. Residents of Quebec may lodge a complaint with the Quebec
        Privacy Commissioner by calling 1-888-528-7741.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Location of data processing</h2>
      <p>All data processing activities undertaken by us take place in the United States.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Third-party websites</h2>
      <p>
        This Website may contain hyperlinks to websites operated by parties other than us. We provide such hyperlinks for your
        reference only. We do not control such websites and are not responsible for their contents or privacy practices. Our
        inclusion of hyperlinks does not imply endorsement of their operators.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Do Not Track</h2>
      <p>
        Do Not Track (“DNT”) is a browser preference that signals websites not to track you. We do not support DNT. You can enable
        or disable DNT by visiting the Preferences or Settings page of your browser.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Transferring data</h2>
      <p>
        We may transfer your personal information for processing to the United States. This means your information may be processed
        outside your country of residence and could be accessible to law enforcement and national security authorities. We use
        standard contractual clauses, additional safeguards, and adequacy decisions when transferring data.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to amend this Privacy Policy at any time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the updated
        Privacy Policy on this Website.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Questions</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
        <a class="text-brand underline" href="mailto:privacy@listwinventures.com">privacy@listwinventures.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
